y^2 = 4px
y = mx + \frac{p}{m}
\left( mx + \frac{p}{m} \right)^2 = m^2x^2 + 2px + \frac{p^2}{m^2} = 4px \\ \Rightarrow m^2x^2 - 2px + \frac{p^2}{m^2} = 0 \\ \Rightarrow \left(mx - \frac{p}{m}\right)^2 = 0
